snippet.textDisplay:
It is no. 3  on songs that I love/admire the most.. the other two being - 
1. Mangal Bhawan Amangal Hari by Ravindra Jain- sadly that version is no longer available on YT, Spotify, JioSaavn 
2. Satguru Mai teri patang by Anil Hanslas… 
If you’re a music lover, you listen to these 3 songs, you’ll understand what True religion is & what secularism is.. What’s God & you might even wanna introspect yourself… 
If you like these 3, I’ll suggest you listen to Arziyan from Delhi 6 and Kun faya kun from Rockstar, pay heed to the lyrics, & I believe you won’t be the same person if you truly understand them.

snippet.textDisplay:
الله غير موجود. إلهنا هو يسوع المسيح. من مات دون أن يكون يسوع مخلصه فهو هالك. أرجوكم لا تؤمنوا ببدعة القرآن. لقد كُتبت بعد 600 عام من الإنجيل على يد كذاب، ومتحرش بالأطفال، وقاتل! اقبلوا يسوع ربًا وإلهًا، وعندها فقط ستدخلون الجنة.
allah ghayr mawjudi. 'iilahuna hu yasue almasihi. man mat dun 'an yakun yasue mukhlisah fahu halka. 'arjukum la tuminuu bibideat alqurani. laqad kutbt baed 600 eam min al'iinjil ealaa yad kadhabi, wamutaharish bial'atfali, waqatili! aiqbiluu yasue rban w'ilhan, waeindaha faqat satadkhulun aljanata.
